 and betrayal, stating that even if he’s cheating, she’ll allow it as he’s always got the taste of her on his lips.\\n\\nThe music video, much like the track, cheekily references many dark satirical movies, such as *’[Ginger Snaps](https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ginger_Snaps_(film)‘*, *’[The Addams Family](https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Addams_Family_(1991_film)’*, & primarily *’[Death Becomes Her](https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death_Becomes_Her)’*, with Ortega playing Madeline, who’s played by [Meryl Streep](https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meryl_Streep), & Carpenter playing Helen, who’s played by [Goldie Hawn](https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Goldie_Hawn)\",\"html\":\"<p>“Taste” is the first track off of Sabrina Carpenter’s sixth studio album, <em>“Short n’ Sweet”<\/em>. It was released as the highly anticipated third single from the album with a music video featuring female actress, <a href=\\\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jenna_Ortega\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">Jenna Ortega<\/a> on August 23rd, 2024, following <a href=\\\"https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/sabrina-carpenter-please-please-please-espresso-number-one-global-charts-1235722059/amp/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">smash hits<\/a> “<a href=\\\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-espresso-lyrics\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/songs/10257779\\\">Espresso<\/a>” &amp; “<a href=\\\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-please-please-please-lyrics\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/songs/10488398\\\">Please Please Please<\/a>”.<\/p>\\n\\n<p>Disco-infused &amp; irresistibly danceable, “Taste” serves as the album’s opener, layering risqué innuendos with revenge and betrayal, stating that even if he’s cheating, she’ll allow it as he’s always got the taste of her on his lips.<\/p>\\n\\n<p>The music video, much like the track, cheekily references many dark satirical movies, such as <em>’<a href=\\\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ginger_Snaps_%28film\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">Ginger Snaps<\/a>‘<\/em>, <em>’<a href=\\\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Addams_Family_%281991_film\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">The Addams Family<\/a>’<\/em>, &amp; primarily <em>’<a href=\\\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death_Becomes_Her\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">Death Becomes Her<\/a>’<\/em>, with Ortega playing Madeline, who’s played by <a href=\\\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meryl_Streep\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">Meryl Streep<\/a>, &amp; Carpenter playing Helen, who’s played by <a href=\\\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Goldie_Hawn\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">Goldie Hawn<\/a><\/p>\"},\"beingCreated\":false,\"apiPath\":\"/annotations/32311307\",\"type\":\"annotation\"}},\"referents\":{\"32311307\":{\"annotations\":[32311307],\"annotatable\":{\"url\":\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-taste-lyrics\",\"type\":\"song\",\"title\":\"Taste\",\"linkTitle\":\"Taste by Sabrina Carpenter\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://images.genius.com/6ecbc2e64e62b35ee2fadf8532056f72.1000x1000x1.png\",\"id\":10628610,\"context\":\"Sabrina Carpenter\",\"clientTimestamps\":{\"lyricsUpdatedAt\":1726508064,\"updatedByHumanAt\":1726508368},\"apiPath\":\"/songs/10628610\"},\"twitterShareMessage\":\"““Taste” is the first track off of Sabrina Carpenter’s sixth studio album, “Short n’ Sweet”. It w…” —@Genius\",\"trackingPaths\":{\"concurrent\":\"/Sabrina-carpenter-taste-lyrics\",\"aggregate\":\"/32311307/Sabrina-carpenter-taste/Taste\"},\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"relationships\":{},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"add_pinned_annotation_to\",\"add_community_annotation_to\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"verifiedAnnotatorIds\":[],\"url\":\"https://genius.com/32311307/Sabrina-carpenter-taste/Taste\",\"songId\":10628610,\"range\":{\"content\":\"Taste\"},\"path\":\"/32311307/Sabrina-carpenter-taste/Taste\",\"isImage\":false,\"isDescription\":true,\"iosAppUrl\":\"genius://referents/32311307\",\"id\":32311307,\"fragment\":\"Taste\",\"classification\":\"unrevie