ript async src=\\\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\\\" charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"><\/script>\\n<\/div>\"},\"type\":\"answer\"},\"811902\":{\"authors\":[{\"user\":8280771,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":1,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"}],\"answerSource\":null,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"edit\",\"destroy\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":11,\"id\":811902,\"hasVoters\":true,\"editorialState\":\"normal\",\"createdAt\":1724385702,\"bodyForEdit\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9Q9OzL_wI8\",\"body\":{\"markdown\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z9Q9OzL_wI8\",\"html\":\"<p><\/p><div class=\\\"embedly_preview embedly_preview--video\\\">\\n<iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" type=\\\"text/html\\\" width=\\\"640\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"1\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/z9Q9OzL_wI8?modestbranding=1&amp;start=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=genius.com\\\"><\/iframe>\\n<\/div>\"},\"type\":\"answer\"},\"812237\":{\"authors\":[{\"user\":8280771,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":1,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"}],\"answerSource\":null,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"edit\",\"destroy\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":16,\"id\":812237,\"hasVoters\":true,\"editorialState\":\"normal\",\"createdAt\":1724457431,\"bodyForEdit\":\">So, \'Taste\' is one of my favorite songs off the album and it says a lot about me and a lot about other people. I think it\'s sort of poking fun of myself a little bit for my mistakes and also poking fun at the, kind of like, facepalm that is life and relationship and the, sort of, situations that it puts you in, um, and it\'s just making lighthearted fun at the whole concept of, you know, people that you\'ve been with moving on to other people, and, you know, I think it\'s a very human thing but it\'s certainly fun.\\n\\n---via [Kiss 108](https://x.com/scanews_/status/1827128756684623964)\",\"body\":{\"markdown\":\">So, \'Taste\' is one of my favorite songs off the album and it says a lot about me and a lot about other people. I think it\'s sort of poking fun of myself a little bit for my mistakes and also poking fun at the, kind of like, facepalm that is life and relationship and the, sort of, situations that it puts you in, um, and it\'s just making lighthearted fun at the whole concept of, you know, people that you\'ve been with moving on to other people, and, you know, I think it\'s a very human thing but it\'s certainly fun.\\n\\n---via [Kiss 108](https://x.com/scanews_/status/1827128756684623964)\",\"html\":\"<blockquote><p>So, ‘Taste’ is one of my favorite songs off the album and it says a lot about me and a lot about other people. I think it’s sort of poking fun of myself a little bit for my mistakes and also poking fun at the, kind of like, facepalm that is life and relationship and the, sort of, situations that it puts you in, um, and it’s just making lighthearted fun at the whole concept of, you know, people that you’ve been with moving on to other people, and, you know, I think it’s a very human thing but it’s certainly fun.<\/p><\/blockquote>\\n\\n<p>—via <a href=\\\"https://x.com/scanews_/status/1827128756684623964\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">Kiss 108<\/a><\/p>\"},\"type\":\"answer\"},\"813837\":{\"authors\":[{\"user\":8280771,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":1,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"}],\"answerSource\":null,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"edit\",\"destroy\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":16,\"id\":813837,\"hasVoters\":true,\"editorialState\":\"normal\",\"createdAt\":1724946991,\"bodyForEdit\":\"https://youtu.be/KLbzKFCOXfs \",\"body\":{\"markdown\":\"https://youtu.be/KLbzKFCOXfs \",\"html\":\"<p><\/p><div class=\\\"embedly_preview embedly_preview--video\\\">\\n<iframe loading=\\\"lazy\\\" type=\\\"text/html\\\" width=\\\"640\\\" height=\\\"390\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" allowfullscreen=\\\"1\\\" src=\\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KLbzKFCOXfs?modestbranding=1&amp;start=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=genius.com\\\"><\/iframe>\\n<\/div>\"},\"type\":\"answer\"},\"814226\":{\"authors\":[{\"user\":8280771,\"pinnedRole\":null,\"attribution\":1,\"type\":\"user_attribution\"}],\"answerSource\":null,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"edit\",\"destroy\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":9,\"id\":814226,\"hasVoters\":true,\"editorialState\":\"normal\",\"createdAt\":1725037589,\"bodyForEdit\":\"\\\"Taste\\\" [debuted](https://x.com/billboardcharts/status/1831015664284233893) at #2 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart during the tracking week ending on August 29, 2024. This marked Sabrina\'s second highest-debut and her second highest-peaking song on the chart. The singer also became the [first soloist](https://www.billboard.com/lists/shaboozey-hot-100-eight-weeks-number-one-sabrina-carpenter-top-10/carpenter-sweetens-nos-2-3-4/?utm_source=twitter&utm_medium=social) to ever chart her first three top five hits in the US simultaneously.\\nIn the UK, \\\"Taste\\\" [debuted](https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/) at #1 on the Official Singles Chart Top 100, which marked Sabrina\'s third #1 on the chart. On the charting week ending on August 29, 2024, Sabrina also became the first female artist in history to simultaneously hold the top 3 on the Official Singles Chart, with [\\\"Please Please Please\\\"](https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-please-please-please-lyrics) at #2 and [\\\"Espresso\\\"](https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-espresso-lyrics) at #3. \",\"body\":{\"markdown\":\"\\\"Taste\\\" [debuted](https://x.com/billboardcharts/status/1831015664284233893) at #2 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart during the tracking week ending on August 29, 2024. This marked Sabrina\'s second highest-debut and her second highest-peaking song on the chart. The singer also became the [first soloist](https://www.billboard.com/lists/shaboozey-hot-100-eight-weeks-number-one-sabrina-carpenter-top-10/carpenter-sweetens-nos-2-3-4/?utm_source=twitter&utm_medium=social) to ever chart her first three top five hits in the US simultaneously.\\nIn the UK, \\\"Taste\\\" [debuted](https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/) at #1 on the Official Singles Chart Top 100, which marked Sabrina\'s third #1 on the chart. On the charting week ending on August 29, 2024, Sabrina also became the first female artist in history to simultaneously hold the top 3 on the Official Singles Chart, with [\\\"Please Please Please\\\"](https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-please-please-please-lyrics) at #2 and [\\\"Espresso\\\"](https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-espresso-lyrics) at #3. \",\"html\":\"<p>“Taste” <a href=\\\"https://x.com/billboardcharts/status/1831015664284233893\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">debuted<\/a> at #2 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart during the tracking week ending on August 29, 2024. This marked Sabrina’s second highest-debut and her second highest-peaking song on the chart. The singer also became the <a href=\\\"https://www.billboard.com/lists/shaboozey-hot-100-eight-weeks-number-one-sabrina-carpenter-top-10/carpenter-sweetens-nos-2-3-4/?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">first soloist<\/a> to ever chart her first three top five hits in the US simultaneously.<br>\\nIn the UK, “Taste” <a href=\\\"https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">debuted<\/a> at #1 on the Official Singles Chart Top 100, which marked Sabrina’s third #1 on the chart. On the charting week ending on August 29, 2024, Sabrina also became the first female artist in history to simultaneously hold the top 3 on the Official Singles Chart, with <a href=\\\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-please-please-please-lyrics\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/songs/10488398\\\">“Please Please Please”<\/a> at #2 and <a href=\\\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-espresso-lyrics\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" data-api_path=\\\"/songs/10257779\\\">“Espresso”<\/a> at #3.<\/p>\"},\"type\":\"answer\"}},\"questions\":{\"1228280\":{\"defaultQuestion\":null,\"author\":8280771,\"answer\":811532,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"iqByAction\":{},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"add_answer\",\"update_answer_source\",\"update\",\"archive\",\"pin\",\"unpin\",\"move\",\"moderate\",\"add_verified_answer\",\"view_qa_page\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":0,\"url\":\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-taste-lyrics/questions/1228280\",\"state\":\"pinned\",\"pinOrder\":262144,\"id\":1228280,\"hasVoters\":false,\"defaultKey\":null,\"createdAt\":1724281436,\"contributorsCount\":1,\"body\":\"Teaser\",\"bagonUrl\":\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-taste-lyrics/questions/1228280\",\"type\":\"question\"},\"1228688\":{\"defaultQuestion\":null,\"author\":8280771,\"answer\":811902,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"iqByAction\":{},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"add_answer\",\"update_answer_source\",\"update\",\"archive\",\"pin\",\"unpin\",\"move\",\"moderate\",\"add_verified_answer\",\"view_qa_page\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":0,\"url\":\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-taste-lyrics/questions/1228688\",\"state\":\"pinned\",\"pinOrder\":131072,\"id\":1228688,\"hasVoters\":false,\"defaultKey\":null,\"createdAt\":1724385702,\"contributorsCount\":1,\"body\":\"Official Lyric Video\",\"bagonUrl\":\"https://genius.com/Sabrina-carpenter-taste-lyrics/questions/1228688\",\"type\":\"question\"},\"1229018\":{\"defaultQuestion\":{\"id\":\"artist_comment:song:10628610\",\"answerPrefix\":null},\"author\":8280771,\"answer\":812237,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"iqByAction\":{},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"add_answer\",\"update_an